<div style="font-size:1.4em; font-weight:bold">Helping with the Documentation</div>
The OpenTTD documentation is stored and edited using this <em>wiki</em>. Feel free to start editing as soon as you feel you can, but '''read the [[Main/en/Manual of Style|Manual of Style]] first''', and make any tests in the [[Main/en/Sandbox|Sandbox]].  

Visit the [[Main/en/Village Pump|village pump]] to discuss any major changes or additions to the documentation, or you can start right in on requests posted in the [[Main/en/Requested Articles|article requests]]. Also:

*Some articles need smaller changes to satisfy our needs, and there is a [[Category/en/To do|list]] of these.  If you don't feel up to writing full articles then this may be a better place to start. 

*There are also some articles that require more work before they can be called finished, and you can browse them in [[Category/en/Articles to be expanded|Expand category]]. 
</div>

